Project Title: Live E-Commerce Electronics Website

LINK : https://l.instagram.com/?u=https%3A%2F%2Fluxeliving.pythonanywhere.com%2F%3Ffbclid%3DPAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAaeYOnCpMHqjK6dQXmCrDAjc2Qe76NpwTpUTHkAqtB97xleRj2FprBvsXm9hOA_aem_5tOhVM23kbdABkR9EzeVfg&e=AT0LeNfL4RJ4B6sMxZ_48JUN3uknVpqe9vFRlfo8xbOR-xatlNphgAM3uzyeQyoGAVKePbijSToDEuR4oJJ0rpPOMb-7R9cE02wUtBw


Description:
This is a fully functional, live-hosted e-commerce platform designed for showcasing and selling electronic products online. The website offers users an interactive and user-friendly interface for browsing, selecting, and purchasing a wide variety of electronic items, such as smartphones, laptops, accessories, and home appliances.

Key Features:

Homepage with Dynamic Product Listings: Displays featured products, promotional banners, and latest arrivals to enhance user engagement.

Product Categories & Filters: Organized product sections (e.g., Mobiles, Laptops, Audio Devices) with filters for price, brand, and specifications for a smooth shopping experience.

Product Details Page: Each product has a dedicated page with images, specifications, pricing, offers, and customer reviews.

Search Functionality: Advanced search bar with keyword suggestions and auto-complete options for easy navigation.

Shopping Cart System: Users can add/remove items, adjust quantities, and view a summary before checkout.

User Authentication: Secure user login and signup system with password encryption and account management.

Order Management: Seamless checkout process, order summary, and confirmation page.

Responsive Design: Optimized for desktops, tablets, and mobile devices for consistent performance across platforms.

Live Hosting: The website is deployed and accessible through a publicly available URL, demonstrating deployment and server management skills.
